1
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:09,720
I heard the Emperor's illness has worsened.

2
00:01:09,720 --> 00:01:12,120
Third Prince, the current situation is unstable.

3
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:14,120
You should return to the palace to take charge.

4
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:16,050
The Marquis will arrange the rest.

5
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:21,160
Zhaohua.

6
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,440
Third Prince.

7
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:24,600
You've changed.

8
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,320
How so?

9
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:29,960
You've become stronger.

10
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:34,520
As expected, he likes the cool and dashing type,

11
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:36,320
who acts with steady composure.

12
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:39,320
Zhaohua, you've learned introspection at such a young age.

13
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:40,520
Even I can't compare.

14
00:01:41,759 --> 00:01:44,080
The Third Prince is definitely starting to admire me.

15
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:45,640
This outfit was the right choice after all.

16
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:47,039
I can't be too flighty when I speak.

17
00:01:47,039 --> 00:01:47,800
Smile less.

18
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:50,280
Speak less to appear steady and deep.

19
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,800
Zhaohua, why are you dressed like this today?

20
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:53,920
I changed my style.

21
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:57,680
By the way, I'm relying on Lord Bai for my return to the palace.

22
00:01:58,039 --> 00:01:59,500
I will convey the message.

23
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:01,040
You two chat first.

24
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,260
I'll take my leave.

25
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,160
From now on,

26
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:13,410
I am the second Sister-in-law.

27
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:30,000
This armor is so heavy.

28
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,880
It's way too heavy.

29
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:40,420
Sister-in-law really did fight her way out of a bloodbath.

30
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,680
Huanghuacai.

31
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:45,600
Sister, are you crazy?

32
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:49,600
Brother, am I looking more and more like Sister-in-law now?

33
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:51,130
Even you mistook me for her.

34
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:54,220
You've been acting very strange lately.

35
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:56,120
Why are you imitating Huanghuacai?

36
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,380
None of your business.

37
00:02:57,920 --> 00:03:00,380
You're even imitating Huanghuacai's walk.

38
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:03,040
You're even lowering your voice to sound like her.

39
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:05,040
Don't you think that's disgusting?

40
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,020
Say that again.

41
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,720
Sister, can you please wake up?

42
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,600
She is her, and you are you.

43
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:13,480
You don't understand. I just want to be better.

44
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,840
That's what he likes.

45
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,960
Then why don't you just change your name too?

46
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,200
Just call yourself Song the Second.

47
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:19,320
You were the one who said I was flighty.

48
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,360
You said I wasn't steady.

49
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,079
Now I've changed.

50
00:03:21,079 --> 00:03:23,360
The Third Prince also thinks I'm different.

51
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,420
What did I do wrong?

52
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,410
Bai Zhaohua.

53
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:29,280
If the Third Prince likes you because you resemble Song Xuan,

54
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,920
then he isn't worth your affection at all.

55
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:34,240
Wronging yourself to throw yourself at a man like this,

56
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,400
is incredibly stupid.

57
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,160
I don't care.

58
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,960
I just want him to see me.

59
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:39,850
Bai Zhaohua.

60
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,560
You are fine just the way you are.

61
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,800
When you act shamelessly and curse,

62
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:46,280
and spout nonsense, that is the real you.

63
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:49,610
You don't have to become Song Xuan to be liked.

64
00:03:50,079 --> 00:03:52,560
If one day the Third Prince truly likes you,

65
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:55,200
he should like the real Bai Zhaohua.

66
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:59,520
But I'm afraid he won't like the real me.

67
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:12,000
Miss, I didn't expect Lord Bai to be so reliable.

68
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,519
You talk too much.

69
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,200
Third Prince.

70
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:20,730
Please take these with you.

71
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:22,280
Song Xuan.

72
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:23,850
And Brother Bai.

73
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:26,520
Thank you for taking care of me these past days.

74
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,280
This is delicious.

75
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,320
This.

76
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:33,640
And this.

77
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:34,640
That's enough.

78
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,370
It won't fit.

79
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:37,560
Sister, you really are thoughtful.

80
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,800
But the palace has everything.

81
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,010
What do you know?

82
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:43,370
This is a token of my affection.

83
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,000
Third Prince, stop putting on airs.

84
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,570
I know you find me noisy.

85
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,880
But I have my reasons.

86
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:51,760
It's better than those who stab you in the back.

87
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:52,490
I don't mind.

88
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,120
Then...

89
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,680
can you stay?

90
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:09,160
Chaohua, actually, I prefer the way you are now.

91
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,730
What are you talking about?

92
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:14,090
I've always been great.

93
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:28,920
Sister-in-law, why did he leave so early?

94
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,280
Princess Tuoya is entering the palace tomorrow.

95
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:33,409
I don't understand.

96
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:36,920
Sister, Princess Tuoya is going to be a concubine.

97
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:40,770
This means the Emperor has agreed to make peace with Yueshi.

98
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:44,200
But wasn't Yueshi's condition for peace the three border cities?

99
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,800
Is the Emperor going senile?

100
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:51,450
I hope the Third Prince can persuade the Emperor.

101
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:59,040
No way.

102
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,890
Can't handle this already?

103
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:05,440
I've always wanted to ask you a question.

104
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:07,920
That Shen Lingbo sends money here every month.

105
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,880
As the dignified daughter of the Prime Minister,

106
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:11,240
why is she so good to you?

107
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,560
Tell me.

108
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,400
What is her relationship with this place?

109
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,000
Do you have something on her?

110
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,650
Or is it something else?

111
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:19,840
Answer me.

112
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,080
Very stubborn.

113
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:28,960
Seems like this place is not simple at all.

114
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,880
Lord Shen, what brings you here?

115
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:39,720
Prince.

116
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:42,170
You're in good spirits.

117
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:45,880
Lord Shen.

118
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,980
Does your Dasheng have anything,

119
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,000
fun to play with besides women?

120
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:52,800
If you like them, Prince,

121
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:55,360
I'll have someone send a few more immediately.

122
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:57,290
You are quite generous, Lord Shen.

123
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,800
We are in the same boat, after all.

124
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,970
Your visit tonight, Lord Shen,

125
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,400
what is it exactly for?

126
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,460
Stop beating around the bush.

127
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,440
She can't hear us.

128
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:10,960
Prince.

129
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:15,520
What about the deal we discussed before?

130
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:18,560
Deal? What deal?

131
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:23,730
Making the Song Family Army disappear from the border completely.

132
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:26,000
I seem to recall something like that.

133
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:28,560
But haven't I already given you a large sum of money?

134
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,760
What more do you want?

135
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:32,120
The Song Family Army is gone.

136
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,720
But the Bai Family Army is still there.

137
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:36,320
The Bai Family Army is just the old, weak, and disabled.

138
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:38,050
I don't consider them a threat.

139
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:40,200
Prince.

140
00:07:41,520 --> 00:07:42,650
Keeping them alive,

141
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:48,680
will always be a thorn in your side.

142
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:52,040
Then what do you want to do, Lord Shen?

143
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:54,700
You just need to help me in secret,

144
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:56,400
and I can help you wipe out

145
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:58,720
all of Yueshi's obstacles in Dasheng.

146
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,720
To get my help,

147
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:05,610
shouldn't you show some sincerity first, Lord Shen?

148
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:07,680
Prince, rest assured.

149
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:10,760
Those who should fall won't escape.

150
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,970
What do you want me to do?

151
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:15,880
Let the Yueshi cavalry stationed outside the city

152
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,290
be under my command.

153
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,640
Once the deed is done,

154
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:23,800
I want the five border cities.

155
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,600
Five... five cities?

156
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,640
Lord Shen.

157
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,840
Three cities are too few.

158
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:31,810
It won't keep my brothers in check.

159
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,960
Besides,

160
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:37,440
Do you have any other choice?

161
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:38,960
Fine.

162
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:41,440
Good.

163
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,039
Also,

164
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,800
I want Shen Lingbo.

165
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,760
What do you want with her?

166
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,280
She is smart.

167
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:51,080
I like smart women.

168
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:55,920
I prefer keeping smart women in dungeons.

169
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:57,720
You want to use her to threaten me.

170
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,200
You flatter yourself.

171
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:01,120
I have no interest in you.

172
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:03,680
I said Shen Lingbo is smart.

173
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,840
Like the sharpest knife.

174
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:09,640
I want to see if I can break this knife.

175
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,720
Lingbo is my daughter!

176
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:17,960
Can you not bear to part with her, Lord Shen?

177
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,920
There are many things in this world

178
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:22,840
more important than family.

179
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,040
Prince,

180
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,760
you must not go back on your word.

181
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:28,120
Rest assured, Lord Shen.

182
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,780
As long as Shen Lingbo is mine,

183
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,880
and the five border cities are mine,

184
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,540
I will never go back on my word.

185
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:34,880
It's a deal.

186
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,600
It's a deal.
